item.title: Data from Litter removal in a tropical rain forest reduces fine root biomass and production but litter addition has few effects
item.description: Sources Rodtassana C, Tanner EVJ (2018) Litter removal in a tropical rain forest reduces fine root biomass and production but litter addition has few effects.
